Minimalistic style: A clean, geometric composition featuring a single green checkmark symbol constructed from folded origami paper, casting a soft shadow on a pure white background. The checkmark appears to be emerging from or sitting atop a neat stack of thin, translucent layered sheets representing code or data. Small abstract geometric shapes in muted blues and grays float nearby, suggesting modularity and components snapping together. The scene has ample negative space, with subtle gradient shadows adding depth. The overall mood is precise, orderly, and satisfying—like puzzle pieces fitting perfectly into place.
